title: Hour 2 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
itunes:title: Hour 2 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
description:
Covino and Rich fill in for Dan Patrick and the crew and start the second hour by putting a spotlight on the New York Mets, specifically Rich starts looking ahead to the playoffs and the conundrum he could find himself in with family, and more!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
